{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1265e86674","title":"江西省波阳县皇岗区东溪乡“文革”中非正常死亡人员档案--方兴田","origin":"根据文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e0a191708","index":0,"year":1986,"month":3,"day":25,"articleId":"1265e86674"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"5275d10348","name":"破四旧","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9073865ccd","name":"江西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"394ec24411","type":"title","text":"江西省波阳县皇岗区东溪乡“文革”中非正常死亡人员档案--方兴田","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"bc4ed68eb6","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名：方兴田","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"00409f31ec","type":"paragraph","text":"性别：男","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"ea7f4b5991","type":"paragraph","text":"籍贯：江西波阳","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"b714025f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"住址：金方扬家恒村","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"0c4c4dfc13","type":"paragraph","text":"1986年3月25日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"63d5b2e1a7","type":"subtitle","text":"关于方兴田在“文革”中非正常死亡情况调查","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"51aacb96c5","type":"subtitle","text":"东溪乡核查小组","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"0c9658cae0","type":"subtitle","text":"1986年3月25日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"16816d48e8","type":"paragraph","text":"死者方兴田，男，现年75岁（死时56岁），文化程度：高小。家庭成份：地主。本人成份：种田。家住东溪乡金方村委会扬家恒村。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"7c7cf1ba0a","type":"paragraph","text":"解放前，方兴田担任本村保长职务，解放后土改期间被划为富农，复查时定为地主，1967年全国都在搞造反有理，破四旧运动，因他家成份是地主，所以他和其他地富一样被抓了起来进行游村批斗、带高帽子，逼他交出金银。67年10月份的一天，早晨9点左右，方兴田和其他地富一道被关在金方老祠堂的戏台上，在红卫兵们的监督下，在各自扎高帽子准备到各村带高帽子游行、批斗，当时正好木匠方文联在戏台上为本村碾屋做木工。9点钟左右是看守交接班的时候，方兴田在别人未注意时，拿走方文联请来帮忙的木匠徐以杰的徒弟的凿子，到戏台里面的柱子旁，把凿子抵在柱子上，自己的颈脖子顶在凿子口上自杀，等别人看到的时候已经晚了，凿子已刺破了喉管，人们才把他的凿子抢走，当时并没有死，立即就把他抬回家中，因他不肯治疗，过了一个星期才死的。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"1f924c5482","type":"paragraph","text":"根据上述调查情况，我们认为方兴田属于自己有一般历史问题自杀，不属逼供讯所致死，无追究他人责任问题。特此报告。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"9c4fa30df9","type":"paragraph","text":" 调查人：徐显明  徐金彬1986年3月29日","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"9f675cd88a","type":"paragraph","text":"经党委审查，同意调查人意见。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"e5312e2c43","type":"paragraph","text":" 86.4.16","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"10f2437e0a","type":"subtitle","text":"询查笔录","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"c133fb58ae","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：86.3.23","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"2162717b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：金方村委会办公室","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"67946034da","type":"paragraph","text":"问姓名等项","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"a15e63c974","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我叫方加兵，男，现年49岁，初小文程，住金方村委会扬家恒村。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"b0256e5e53","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你是方兴田的什么人？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"79ceb7ee72","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我是他的儿子，现在唯一的一个儿子。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"5b01c866f0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你父亲死的事你知道吗？","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"7ec243aef4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我知道。当时是在67年下半年，我有29岁了。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"efc8720b46","type":"paragraph","text":"问：请你把你父亲当时的情况谈一下。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"ea4ef2ad20","type":"paragraph","text":"答：当时是搞造反有理期间，有人说我家有金银，就把我父亲抓了去，把我关在家里，我父亲被抓去后，被人用开水浇背，硬逼交出金银，我关在家里也受惩。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"8ba04e12a5","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你父亲被用开水烫，你看见吗？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"3478ed858e","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我没看见。是听见方兴富等人讲的，当时他也是被关在那里。他还说用开水浇后再用冷水浇，浇了之后下来就带了一层肉来。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"69d904a942","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你父亲是为什么事死的。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"6a1e26c891","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我父亲是受不住那些刑罚而自杀的。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"fd65cc4f87","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他是怎样死的？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"46feefd4e8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是用凿子刺喉管而死的。当时刺的时候没有死，是过了一个星期后才死的。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"2357e315f6","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你父亲死前对你说了什么？","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"38782c89b4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有说什么。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"ccf020c71a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你还知道些什么？","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"d895c0d5d9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：其它我不清楚，因为当时我也是被人管押着的。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"cb136e1934","type":"paragraph","text":"问：以上属实吗？","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"a0afcf375d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是实事。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"112fa09a0d","type":"paragraph","text":"问：方兴富现在在世吗？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"f47293082a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：已死了。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"dbe7d92f3d","type":"paragraph","text":" 口述人：方加兵","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"7bec55055b","type":"subtitle","text":"调查笔录","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"c411b495fc","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：86.3.23","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"6d9545b31b","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：金方村委会办公室","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"0a185be8be","type":"paragraph","text":"问姓名等项","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"c15a3a4b7a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我叫方庆升，男，52岁，住金方村委会扬家恒村。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"54789a2017","type":"paragraph","text":"问：关于方兴田在文革中死的原因你知道吗？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"727948f345","type":"paragraph","text":"答：知道。当时我是民兵营长。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"1fbdf7c84c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你谈谈方兴田死的情况。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"ed4f801bf1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他是自己由凿子刺伤的，后一个星期左右才死的。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"071c1256c3","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他为什么事而死？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"6bd2e1ec46","type":"paragraph","text":"答：据他说是受不了批斗挨打。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"745b0d9fca","type":"paragraph","text":"问：对他实行过什么惩罚？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"b72356ae85","type":"paragraph","text":"答：也没有进行过特殊手段，都是与其他地富一样批斗游村、带高帽子等。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"aca33c7515","type":"paragraph","text":"问：是不是对他进行过浇开水惩罚？","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"8e49672d93","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。因他是穷地主，对一些富地主还进行过浇冷水的惩罚。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"0e79299c19","type":"paragraph","text":"问：发生的事是在什么时间？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"fff67c855e","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是在67年10月份左右。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"6591ede648","type":"paragraph","text":"问：其它还有什么事？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"37edf6868d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有什么。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"},{"id":"3dc1fd8fac","type":"paragraph","text":" 口述人：方庆升调查人：徐金彬、徐显明笔录人：徐显明","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674"}],"page":{"id":"1f48cfe1fa","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1265e86674","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}